* Diana looked towards Rion, almost sure that he would know just who she 
was.
Her form may have changed, but her signature was one in the same.
She took a step towards him, feeling all the open cuts from her attack.
But then she suddenly saw the stance which Rion was taking, and she 
remembered it from whay back when they were playing and his guard came 
along, making himself seem tough and commanding when he had been told that 
it was time to go and he wanted to stay and play more. Just saying to the 
guard that he was going to stay.
She almost smiled at the thought.
Then he would get carted away towards his parents with the appointment to 
play later.

Diana only shook her head and sighed. Boys!
She took another step towards Rion and then another until she was standing 
right in front of him. Looking right into his eyes, hers hard as when she 
use to play fight with him.
Diana lifted a paw and poked it at Rions stomach.*

" You look like a giant pin cushen. You know that? "

* She then wiggled her paw, she knew his ticklish spots.*
